<br>
I am a Halfling warrior of Rallos Zek.  Under the alignment system, I started as Discord Neutral, can changed to (True) Neutral after reaching 10, actually 15 I think.  Mainly because I was an officer or Order of the Oaken, and I felt that the responsabilities of an officer would curb the Discordant tendencies.  At any rate, per the alignment system, Halflings could not be evil, as it was against their nature.  <br>
<br>
With the release of PoP, I come to find that NPCs in PoK see me as Evil, and constantly suggest I should move to the dark side of town, and warn me about using the portals in the good side of town.  Good and evil in PoK seems to be defined by your god.  It would now seem that Halflings, at least those who follow Rallos Zek, can be evil.<br>
